{"id":434178,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/04/吕楠：被遗忘的人-中国精神病人生存状况/","date":"2016-04-05T18:57:28Z","modified":"2016-04-05T19:00:03Z","title":"吕楠：被遗忘的人——中国精神病人生存状况","content":"<p>医院外面才是精神病院，而真正的精神病院里面倒像教堂、寺庙、修道院，极为宁静。——吕楠</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434179\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.58.52.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 上午11.58.52\" width=\"460\" height=\"651\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.58.52.png 460w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.58.52-212x300.png 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p>这是一个盲人患者。当他感到有人在他面前时，便会重复说：“他们欺负我。”</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434180\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.22.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 上午11.59.22\" width=\"491\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.22.png 491w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.22-300x202.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 491px) 100vw, 491px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434181\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.29.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 上午11.59.29\" width=\"484\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.29.png 484w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.29-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 484px) 100vw, 484px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p>张树华（右）, 38岁, 住院两个多月, 由于没人帮她翻身和擦洗，屁股上的褥疮已有拳头般大小。拍照十天后，她死于医院。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434182\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.35.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 上午11.59.35\" width=\"482\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.35.png 482w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.35-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 482px) 100vw, 482px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434183\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.41.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 上午11.59.41\" width=\"480\" height=\"318\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.41.png 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.41-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p>从1989年开始，吕楠用15年的时间完成了他恢宏如史诗般的“三部曲”：《被遗忘的人-中国精神病人生存状况》、《在路上-中国天主教》和《四季-西藏农民的日常生活》三个系列作品。这三部作品“仿佛象征了人类今天的精神状况，象征了吕楠期望的人类伟大精神的复归”(栗宪庭语)。 15年，吕楠如苦行僧一般生活、工作和学习，他坚信“好东西是在沉默中完成的”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434184\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.46.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 上午11.59.46\" width=\"481\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.46.png 481w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.46-300x198.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 481px) 100vw, 481px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 黑龙江 1989</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434185\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.53.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 上午11.59.53\" width=\"487\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.53.png 487w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.53-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 487px) 100vw, 487px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 北京 1989</p>\n<p>女孩,11岁。由于缺少儿童病房，中国绝大部分儿童患者只能同成年病人住在一起。这些成年病人不仅不会照顾他们，有时还会打他们。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434186\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.59.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 上午11.59.59\" width=\"480\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.59.png 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-上午11.59.59-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434187\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.06.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.00.06\" width=\"475\" height=\"319\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.06.png 475w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.06-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 家庭  北京 1989</p>\n<p>张夏平，27岁，云南人。北京办画展期间住在朋友家，画展闭幕当天精神病复发，朋友认为她装病要赶她出门，“人们应当理解我，我是个病人。”她哭着说。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434188\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.12.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.00.12\" width=\"484\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.12.png 484w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.12-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 484px) 100vw, 484px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 北京 1989</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434189\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.20.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.00.20\" width=\"484\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.20.png 484w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.20-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 484px) 100vw, 484px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 家庭 四川 1990</p>\n<p>谢致梅（右）一家四口，妻子（左）及二个孩子都是精神病患者。照片是他死去的儿子，而躺在医院破屋里的女儿谢群英已奄奄一息。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434190\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.28.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.00.28\" width=\"480\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.28.png 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.28-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434191\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.35.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.00.35\" width=\"483\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.35.png 483w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.35-300x202.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 483px) 100vw, 483px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 家庭  四川 1990</p>\n<p>陶世茂，22岁，村里唯一的大学生。寒假回家首次发病，杀死母亲，打伤父亲（左）。恐惧的家人把他关进石头房。每天为他送饭的是最疼他的85岁的奶奶。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434192\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.42.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.00.42\" width=\"487\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.42.png 487w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.00.42-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 487px) 100vw, 487px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 贵州 1990</p>\n<p>医院没有院子，病人白天中的大部分时间都是在斜坡上度过。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434193\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.13.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.02.13\" width=\"481\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.13.png 481w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.13-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 481px) 100vw, 481px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 黑龙江 1989</p>\n<p>打扑克的患者，输的一方要接受顶枕头的处罚。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434194\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.19.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.02.19\" width=\"487\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.19.png 487w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.19-300x204.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 487px) 100vw, 487px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 陕西 1990</p>\n<p>1989年到1990年，吕楠跨越十多个省市拍摄了他“三部曲”中的第一部：《被遗忘的人-中国精神病人生存状况》，以全景方式关注了中国精神病人的生活，不仅是医院，吕楠还拍摄了家庭中，以及流浪中的病人。在吕楠的照片中，这些精神病人从被社会妖魔化了的概念形象中复活，重新变成多种多样的，活生生的，有着所有人都具备有的喜怒哀乐、爱恋和亲情的正常“人”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434195\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.26.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.02.26\" width=\"324\" height=\"485\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.26.png 324w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.26-200x300.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 324px) 100vw, 324px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 四川 1990</p>\n<p>谢致梅的女儿谢群英，24岁。她家付给医院的住院费已用完，医院便把她从正式病房搬到这间废弃的屋子，她的生命已奄奄一息。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434196\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.32.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.02.32\" width=\"326\" height=\"482\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.32.png 326w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.32-203x300.png 203w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 326px) 100vw, 326px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1990</p>\n<p>她不会说话，警察3年前街上捡的。她有破坏欲，医院不能提供衣褥，一天大部分时间她都躺在地上，确切说是躺在自己屎尿混合物上。半年后死在医院。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434197\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.40.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.02.40\" width=\"323\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.40.png 323w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.40-203x300.png 203w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 323px) 100vw, 323px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 广西 1990</p>\n<p>这是医院的重患者病房，这样的病房在这有十几间。23岁的周举铎，住院已超过一个月，但从没有离开过13号病房。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434198\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.47.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.02.47\" width=\"324\" height=\"484\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.47.png 324w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.47-201x300.png 201w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 324px) 100vw, 324px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 云南 1990</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434199\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.54.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.02.54\" width=\"319\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.54.png 319w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.02.54-201x300.png 201w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 319px) 100vw, 319px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p>万有胜，40岁，小学美术教师，墙上挂的是他画的雷锋像。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434201\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.06.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.03.06\" width=\"330\" height=\"481\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.06.png 330w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.06-206x300.png 206w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 330px) 100vw, 330px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津1989</p>\n<p>陈金铭，45岁，住院已有五年。二十年前在家里发病时长时间待在雪中，部分手指和全部脚趾被冻掉。</p>\n<p>此前，这组照片从未在国内完整的发表过，但它仍然引起巨大反响，上世纪90年代初，这些照片经过各种途径流传，影响了一批年轻的中国摄影师。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434202\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.12.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.03.12\" width=\"485\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.12.png 485w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.12-300x204.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 485px) 100vw, 485px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 洗澡的病人 天津 1989</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434203\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.17.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.03.17\" width=\"486\" height=\"327\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.17.png 486w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.17-300x202.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 486px) 100vw, 486px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 家庭  贵州 1990</p>\n<p>贾文英，39岁，她的丈夫二个月前去世。现在，她和女儿以乞讨为生。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434204\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.23.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.03.23\" width=\"483\" height=\"327\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.23.png 483w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.23-300x203.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 483px) 100vw, 483px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 家庭 四川 1990</p>\n<p>王建国，40岁，患病已超过20年。他唯一的依靠是81岁的母亲。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434205\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.28.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.03.28\" width=\"492\" height=\"328\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.28.png 492w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.28-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 四川 1990</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434206\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.34.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.03.34\" width=\"485\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.34.png 485w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.34-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 485px) 100vw, 485px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p>韩民，36岁，住院已6年。他父亲把每月收入的一半支付其住院费。近日，韩民的哥哥被查出肝癌。“我都不知道该救哪一个好了”韩民的父亲叹息道。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434207\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.40.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.03.40\" width=\"483\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.40.png 483w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.40-300x202.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 483px) 100vw, 483px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 黑龙江 1989</p>\n<p>为室友画画</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434208\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.45.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.03.45\" width=\"483\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.45.png 483w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.03.45-300x202.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 483px) 100vw, 483px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 家庭 贵州 1990</p>\n<p>唐明季，45岁，丈夫于九年前去世。家里的门窗已被她取下用于取暧做饭。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434209\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.11.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.05.11\" width=\"470\" height=\"318\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.11.png 470w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.11-300x203.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 家庭 云南 1990</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434210\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.18.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.05.18\" width=\"478\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.18.png 478w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.18-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 北京 1989</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434211\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.24.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.05.24\" width=\"489\" height=\"329\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.24.png 489w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.24-300x202.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 489px) 100vw, 489px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 黑龙江 1989</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434212\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.29.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.05.29\" width=\"483\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.29.png 483w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.29-300x201.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 483px) 100vw, 483px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434213\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.35.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.05.35\" width=\"490\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.35.png 490w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.35-300x203.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px\" /></p>\n<p>▲ 精神病院 天津 1989</p>\n<p>孟兆兰，66岁，住院超过十年。因肥胖医院没有适合的衣服，她左半身偏瘫已6年，为她擦身的是和她一样的病人。“为我照张像吧，”她说：“我快要死了。”</p>\n<p>而吕楠的影像中，虽有视觉冲击的画面，但是摄影师却没有刻意营造不安、可悲、恐怖的景象。相反他在实际接触过病人后，着力于展现病人们真实平凡的一面，在今天看来或许你会觉得很合理，但是在25年前这些影像深深影响着后来者。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434214\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.46.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.05.46\" width=\"476\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.46.png 476w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.46-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 476px) 100vw, 476px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434215\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.52.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.05.52\" width=\"477\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.52.png 477w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.52-300x192.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 477px) 100vw, 477px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434216\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.59.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.05.59\" width=\"473\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.59.png 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.05.59-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434217\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.06.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.06.06\" width=\"479\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.06.png 479w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.06-300x197.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.06-230x150.png 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 479px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434218\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.11.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.06.11\" width=\"475\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.11.png 475w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.11-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434219\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.16.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.06.16\" width=\"473\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.16.png 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.16-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434220\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.22.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.06.22\" width=\"476\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.22.png 476w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.22-300x197.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.22-230x150.png 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 476px) 100vw, 476px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434221\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.29.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.06.29\" width=\"475\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.29.png 475w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.29-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434222\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.35.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-05 at 下午12.06.35\" width=\"474\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.35.png 474w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/Screen-Shot-2016-04-05-at-下午12.06.35-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px\" /></p>\n<p>新闻数据显示，目前全中国有超过一亿的精神病患者，撇除政治问题，如上访者被关进精神病院、社会对于有关疾病的教育与治疗等仍需要继续关注。在摄影师的镜头下，展现了这些病人的真实面目和处境。</p>\n","author":996,"categories":[18270,18269,9203,10466],"tags":[9071,12722,9551,30737]}